name: Stuffed tiger amigurumi toy
description: This stuffed crochet tiger doll is my personal favorite. He is my absolute best work so far. The legs are pose-able, he sits on his own, and he stands, however he must be held standing unless you prop his tail against something. He would make an awesome child's toy, or a beautiful decoration. This tiger is so lovable and ready to be shipped to your door!

name: Espeon Plush Pokemon Amigurumi 8" tall
description:
Espeon is from the cartoon and trading card game, Pokemon. He is made in the style of Amigurumi, which is crocheting in the round to create closed 3D shapes. This Espeon is already made ready to go. Expect 3-5 days for shipping.
From the bottom of his paw to the tips of the ears is 8" tall. 
His tail has a pipe cleaner in it making it flexible for positioning.

name: Umbreon Plush Pokemon Amigurumi 8-9" tall
description:
Umbreon is from the cartoon and trading card game, Pokemon. He is made in the style of Amigurumi, which is crocheting in the round to create closed 3D shapes. From time of purchase, it takes about 2 days processing before item will be shipped, and then 3-5 days for shipping.
From tip of his ears to his paw is 8-9". Difference is based on ear height.

name: Little Stuffed Elephant
description: This is a crocheted amigurumi elephant. He is about the size of a beanie baby. He's made of redheart yarn, fiberfill and plastic safety eyes. He's very cuddly!

name: Little Stuffed Fox
description: This stuffed toy is a cuddly crocheted amigurumi fox. He's made of 100% acrylic yarn, fiberfill and plastic safety eyes. Spot cleaning only is recommended for washing. Great for playing with or for decoration purposes.
